					<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
						<h2 class="section-title text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 inline-block relative" data-i18n="about.strength.section.title">Our Strength</h2>
						<p class="section-subtitle text-xl text-gray-400" data-i18n="about.strength.section.subtitle">What sets us apart in the AI landscape</p>
